-O quê?

716
00:51:41,181 --> 00:51:42,224
Justin.

717
00:51:43,767 --> 00:51:44,727
Mãe?

718
00:51:45,227 --> 00:51:46,145
Justin! Não.

719
00:51:46,520 --> 00:51:48,314
