Eu prometo.

728
00:52:13,047 --> 00:52:14,048
Jessica.

729
00:52:14,631 --> 00:52:16,175
Nós o pegamos. Pegamos o Bryce.

730
00:52:16,717 --> 00:52:18,093
Mas pegaram o Justin também.

731
00:52:20,054 --> 00:52:21,597
